<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٧٩٧ - ش ر خ]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شرَخَ١ يَشرُخ، شروخًا، فهو شارِخ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• شرَخ الصبيُّ:</span> بلغ أوّلَ شبابه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• شرَخ نابُ البعير:</span> شقَّ اللّحمَ وظهرَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>